{"tid":238532,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"冇錢真係唔好學人結婚","createTime":"2017-05-11T05:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T05:28:27.000Z","uid":32500,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe8b0bb360e28a0a28c623f7f72c60da7cd2bf1e","tid":238532,"uid":32500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"咁小弟今年廿七，同老婆結左婚兩年，咁小弟一個月搵得萬七，平時都比老婆屌到仆街，話嫁錯比我，仲成日拎我同佢個獸醫ex比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我都知我冇出色，每個月搵幾多扣埋食飯撘車，全部上繳，仲要就哂佢，咁我身為男人，間唔中都有性需要，但佢從來都冇理過我，淨係叫我自己打飛機，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁尋日小弟放工返到屋企，遲左十幾分鐘同唔記得覆佢what屎app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁佢一埋牙就屌我老母，問我係咪去叫雞，屌到我仆街，咁我就話大佬十幾分鐘咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊黎得切啊。<br />\n呢個時間，我見到佢望住我細佬二百五，偷偷地講左句死牙簽佬，叫雞都派報紙，呢一刻我真係忍唔住，一部iphone 掉埋去，然後捉住佢沖左入房大戰三百回合，屌到佢係咁嗌唔好停唔好停<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依加我係廚房洗緊碗，佢話見我表現唔錯，賞左一百蚊比我，我想問各位巴絲邊度整iphone平呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f827be35292c7d003776fc290842a4371768bb","tid":238532,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31fd405a68d8464707aaa56ec1dc3338b60199a9","tid":238532,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"e2f7eca800c8c8134a84dff144b4084b78dceaac","tid":238532,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"ok 有新意<br />\n7/10"},{"pid":"c8b6df3af9059858ad3b1f24f6ab0fe8094cc5ec","tid":238532,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"6分"},{"pid":"d4e0bb97e2e6807954f1f192b437f23431bd66c0","tid":238532,"uid":32500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺同一間屋send咩what屎app?<br />\n再作過啦</blockquote><br />\n佢what屎app問我幾時返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b714e748fe13cff09253d4e2e189a7828cd9dab","tid":238532,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"日日都有連登仔出 post 抹黑香港女仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1910e73f8ae1b60f592e0bc3414424b6a6795a2","tid":238532,"uid":32500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日都有連登仔出 post 抹黑香港女仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係抹黑，我老婆堅正，68kg，樣似欣宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要細細粒🤤"}]}